'''瑞士邮政'''（{{lang-fr|La Poste Suisse}}，{{lang-it|La Posta Svizzera}}，{{lang-de|Die Schweizerische Post}}，{{lang-rm|La Posta Svizra}}）是[[瑞士|瑞士]]的邮政部门，由瑞士联邦所拥有。它是瑞士國内第二大雇主<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.post.ch/en/index/uk_ueber_uns/uk_konzern.htm | title=A public-sector company | publisher=Swiss Post | accessdate=2006-06-16 | archive-date=2006-08-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060825071842/http://www.post.ch/en/index/uk_ueber_uns/uk_konzern.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>，總部位于[[伯爾尼|伯爾尼]]。<ref>"[http://www.post.ch/en/post-gb-2009.pdf Annual Report 2009] {{Wayback|url=http://www.post.ch/en/post-gb-2009.pdf |date=20120306012514 }}." Swiss Post. 224/244. Retrieved on 7 December 2010. "Swiss Post Viktoriastrasse 21 P.O. Box 3030 Berne Switzerland."</ref><ref>"[http://www.post.ch/en/post-startseite/post-konzern/post-konzern-uebersicht/post-politik-wirtschaft/post-politik-wirtschaft-kontakt.htm Contact] {{Wayback|url=http://www.post.ch/en/post-startseite/post-konzern/post-konzern-uebersicht/post-politik-wirtschaft/post-politik-wirtschaft-kontakt.htm |date=20120323023145 }}." Swiss Post. Retrieved on 7 December 2010. "Viktoriastrasse 21 3030 Bern."</ref>

